<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٦٣ ... سُورَةُ المُنَافِقُونَ ... آياتها ١١ مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جُنَّةً}</span> ... وِقَايَةً وَسُتْرَةً لَهُمْ مِنَ المُؤَاخَذَةِ وَالعَذَابِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آمَنُوا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> فِي الظَّاهِرِ لَا غَيْرُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَطُبِعَ}</span> ... خُتِمَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَا يَفْقَهُونَ}</span> ... لَا يَفْهَمُونَ مَا فِيهِ صَلَاحُهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَسْمَعْ لِقَوْلِهِمْ}</span> ... تَسْمَعْ لِحَدِيثِهِمْ؛ لِفَصَاحَتِهِمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَأَنَّهُمْ خُشُبٌ مُّسَنَّدَةٌ}</span> ... كَأَنَّهُمْ لِخُلُوِّ قُلُوبِهِمْ مِنَ الإِيمَانِ،<span class="c5"> وَعُقُولِهِمْ مِنَ الفَهْمِ:</span> أَخْشَابٌ مُلْقَاةٌ عَلَى حَائِطٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَحْسَبُونَ}</span> ... يَظُنُّونَ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كُلَّ صَيْحَةٍ عَلَيْهِمْ}</span> ... كُلَّ صَوْتٍ عَالٍ وَاقِعًا عَلَيْهِمْ؛ لِعِلْمِهِمْ بِحَقِيقَةِ حَالِهِمْ، وَلِخَوْفِهِمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَاتَلَهُمُ اللَّهُ}</span> ... أَخْزَاهُمْ، وَطَرَدَهُمْ مِنَ رَحْمَتِهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَنَّى يُؤْفَكُونَ}</span> ... كَيْفَ يُصْرَفُونَ عَنِ الإِيمَانِ بَعْدَ قِيَامِ البُرْهَانِ؟!<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَوَّوْا رُؤُوسَهُمْ}</span> ... عَطَفُوهَا إِعْرَاضًا، وِاسْتِهْزَاءً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَصُدُّونَ}</span> ... يُعْرِضُونَ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَنفَضُّوا}</span> ... يَتَفَرَّقُوا عَنْهُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَّجَعْنَا}</span> ... مِنْ غَزْوَةِ بَنِي المُصْطَلِقِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>